**Professional Profile**
NGUYEN TRUNG THANG is an aspiring Machine Learning Engineer with a robust foundation in deep learning and AI project development. While possessing 0 years of formal professional experience, Thang has actively led and contributed to significant team projects. These include developing a Visual Question Answering system utilizing generative AI and custom CNN-LSTM-Attention models, and an OCR pipeline combining CNNs and Transformer Decoders for text extraction. Thang also demonstrated expertise in natural language processing by training and fine-tuning ViT5 and BartPho models for Vietnamese text correction, showcasing practical application of PyTorch and TensorFlow for model optimization.

**Core Skills & Technology**
Proficient in Python, PyTorch, TensorFlow, Keras, and HuggingFace Transformers. Additional technical skills encompass Scikit-learn, OpenCV, Pandas, Django, and Linux.

**Education & Certifications**
Thang is currently pursuing a Bachelor of Computer Science from Ton Duc Thang University, with an expected graduation in 2025. Furthermore, Thang holds an Aptis ESOL Certificate, achieving a score of 154/200.